data.title: Living in Belgrade, January 2013 (PTSA)
data.meta_description: Living in Belgrade, January 2013 (PTSA) - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document provides information for living in Belgrade, Serbia. It includes sections on general information about Belgrade's history and climate, useful tips on Serbian habits and customs like greetings, business lunches, and paying bills, as well as information on necessities, transportation, shopping, services, leisure activities, and places to find more information.
